::Striker::

Striker jumps upward, his jetpack blasting him up at full strength. The 
spikes hit his leg, tearing a huge gash through it. The Maximal growls as 
mech fluid spills from his leg.

He turns to Savage, pulling out a rifle and firing at the bot with it, along 
with his shoulder blasters.
